      <body>This patch makes it possible to use :if and :unless together when using callbacks and allows you to add multiple conditions as an array.

Example:
@@@ ruby
  before_validation :set_random_user, :unless =&gt; :user, :if =&gt; :beginning
  validate :validates_user, :if =&gt; [:user, :beginning]
